Spontaneous compartment syndrome and endovascular repair of tibioperoneal trunk 
pseudoaneurysm in Ehlers-Danlos syndrome.

Choinski KN(1), Ilonzo N(1), Tadros RO(1), Olin JW(2)(3), Phair J(1).

Author information:
(1)Division of Vascular Surgery, Icahn School of Medicine at Mount Sinai, New 
