Cost-effectiveness and budget impact of venetoclax in combination with rituximab 
in relapsed/refractory chronic lymphocytic leukemia in Switzerland.

Barbier M(1), Durno N(2), Bennison C(2), Örtli M(3), Knapp C(3), Schwenkglenks 
